Step 5: Store Data in SQLite Database

Creates datascienceproject.db with tables:

Table Name	Description
cryptocurrencies	Crypto metadata
crypto_prices	Historical crypto prices
oil_prices	Oil prices
stock_prices	Stock index prices
combined_stocks_prices	Merged stock data
Step 6: Streamlit Application

The app provides:

ğŸ“Š Market Overview Dashboard

