ğŸ›  How to Run This Project Locally
1. Clone the Repository
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/cross-market-analysis.git
cd cross-market-analysis

2. Install Dependencies
pip install pandas requests yfinance streamlit plotly

3. Run the Data Pipeline
python cross_market_analysis.py


This will:

Fetch data

Create the database

Store all tables

4. Run the Streamlit App
streamlit run app.py

